_assets/steam/apps/2115620/extras/7对象侦测.jpg?t=1754574262\" /></span></h2></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >精准实现您的影音创意</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关键画格</h2>精确定位、缩放和旋转对象，随心所欲操控客制化动画。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115620/extras/8关键画格.JPG?t=1754574262\" /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >运动摄影</h2>简单点击几下，即可运用预设镜头消除鱼眼变形、稳定晃动影片、定格、或改变影片速度，完美捕捉并重现每个精彩时刻。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115620/extras/10运动摄影.jpg?t=1754574262\" /></span></h2></ul>",
